Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:19.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,平凡的三年級小學生\N\N高町奈葉與命運意外邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:24.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,繼承旭日的勇氣　獲得了魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:30.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,在魔法指引下的邂逅\N\N究竟是偶然還是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,儘管現在還不知道答案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:38.93,Default1,,0,0,0,,魔法少女奈葉　要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:41.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,「太古遺產」就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,形狀是藍色的寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:51.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,通稱「聖石之種」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:59.81,Default1,,0,0,0,,是的　馬上就可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:11.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,第四話\N\N「敵手！？　另一位魔法少女！」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,來　尤諾　過來過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:22.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,真乖真乖　尤諾好聰明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:26.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉　還沒準備好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:30.13,Default1,,0,0,0,,對不起　馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,咦？　今天要出門嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.36,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯　到月村家去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:39.19,Default1,,0,0,0,,鈴鹿請奈葉過去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,哦　是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:45.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,那麼阿恭是要去見阿忍吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:49.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯　順便去見一面啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,那就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,不然就趕不上公車了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.89,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤諾君　過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,你們路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:09.81,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.24,Default1,,0,0,0,,我們出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:33.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,今天要在鈴鹿家裡開茶會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:37.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,我要與愛麗莎和鈴鹿共度週末
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:42.92,Default1,,0,0,0,,哥哥則去見鈴鹿的姊姊阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:50.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:12.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,恭也先生　奈葉小姐　歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯　承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.37,Default1,,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,這位是月村家女傭長　諾愛爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:24.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,雖然話不多　卻是個大美人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:27.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉　恭也哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,鈴鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.88,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉　歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:03.92,Default1,,0,0,0,,這位是琺琳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:08.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,鈴鹿的貼身女傭　是個溫柔開朗的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.55,Default1,,0,0,0,,恭也　歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.35,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:18.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,哥哥與阿忍姊姊是高中時代的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,現在兩人非常親密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,我去準備茶水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,兩位想喝些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.07,Default1,,0,0,0,,就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,我也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:33.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,琺琳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,是　明白了　姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,我和恭也就回房間去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,好的　我稍後送到房間去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:51.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.64,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯　早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:58.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,鈴鹿的姊姊和奈葉的哥哥好親熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:08.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,姊姊認識了恭也哥哥後　總是那麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:12.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,我的哥哥…　不知怎樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:22.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,不過　與從前相比\N\N似乎變得更體貼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,而且變得很常笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:33.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:41.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,對了　今天多謝你的邀請了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:46.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,哪裡　我很高興你能來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,今天你看起來很有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:55.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉最近一直無精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:02.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,如果有什麼心事　能不能告訴我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.25,Default1,,0,0,0,,我們倆都很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:08.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,鈴鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.13,Default1,,0,0,0,,愛麗莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:23.25,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤諾君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,愛　不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是草莓奶茶和奶油起司餅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,琺琳　危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,安全了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:07.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,鈴鹿　奈葉　對不起{\fnSimHei}～{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,她又出事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,真拿她沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:35.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,鈴鹿家果真是貓的天堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:40.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,小貓們真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:44.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,有幾隻已找到了飼主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.72,Default1,,0,0,0,,很快就要告別了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.31,Default1,,0,0,0,,是嗎…　有些捨不得呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:56.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,不過　能看著它們長大　我還是很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:29.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:32.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:35.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:37.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤諾君？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,哦呀　尤諾怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,或許是發現什麼東西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,我…　我去把它找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:51.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,我也一起去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.24,Default1,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,很快就回來了　你們等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:14.92,Default1,,0,0,0,,發動了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,這裡太引人注目了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,必須設置結界才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,結界…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,就是與我們最初見面時的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:29.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,以此改變魔法空間與通常空間的時流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是我比較擅長的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,結界空間不會太廣闊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.64,Default1,,0,0,0,,但應該足以覆蓋這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:32.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,那…　那…　那…　那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,大…　大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:41.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,那隻小貓想長大的心願　被準確地實現了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,是…　是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,不過　這樣會很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:51.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,得儘快將它恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,是…　是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:57.88,Default1,,0,0,0,,長得這麼大　鈴鹿也會為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,看來它沒有敵意…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.64,Default1,,0,0,0,,就趕快封印好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:10.89,Default1,,0,0,0,,旭日之心！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,雷光戰斧　光子靈槍連擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:24.74,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Photon Lancer Full Autofire{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}光子靈槍·FA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:35.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,魔…　魔力光！？　怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,旭日之心　拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.50,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Standby Ready{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:42.50,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1320)\t(\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&)}Set up{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.53,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Flier Fin{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}翔空羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.83,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Wide Area Protection{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}廣域防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:05.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,魔導師…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.61,Default1,,0,0,0,,這些都已不再令我吃驚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:28.45,Default1,,0,0,0,,或許我已沒什麼可再教給奈葉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:40.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,同類的魔導師…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,是太古遺產的搜索者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:51.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,不會錯的　她也來自我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:55.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,而且　這個女孩…　她知道聖石之種的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:02.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,與「雷光戰斧」相同的智慧型魔導器…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,雷光…　戰斧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:12.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,太古遺產…　聖石之種…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.36,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Scythe Form Set up{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}光鐮形態　啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,對不起　我要把它帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.35,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Evasion{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}回避
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.60,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Flier Fin{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}翔空羽翼
