Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:57.41,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H8000BB&)}Protection{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:00.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:13.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,為什麼要這樣…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:19.04,Default1,,0,0,0,,就算回答你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,恐怕…　也沒什麼意義…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.19,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Devise Form{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}魔杖形態
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.82,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Shooting Mode{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}射擊模式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.16,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Divine Buster Standby{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}天神烈破　準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.03,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Photon Lancer Get set{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}光子靈槍　準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:46.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,她的年紀一定與我相仿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:50.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,美麗的雙眼與美麗的長髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:53.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,可是　這個女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.32,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Fire{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}發射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:17.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:51.92,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Sealing Form Set up{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}封印形態　啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:02.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:26.53,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Order{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}請指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:31.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,太古遺產──聖石之種　No.XIV
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:33.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,封印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:34.56,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Yes sir{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:57.92,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Sealing{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}封印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:17.57,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Captured{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:11.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,醒來的時候　天空已被晚霞染紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:16.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,是尤諾君將哥哥他們帶了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:20.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,我向大家撒謊說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:24.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,尋找尤諾君時不小心摔倒暈了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:30.71,Default1,,0,0,0,,害大家這麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:34.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,真是很過意不去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:46.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,她的魔導杖　穿著　還有魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:49.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,或許…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:54.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,不　她一定是來自我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:22:05.98,Default1,,0,0,0,,只要繼續收集聖石之種\N\N就還會與她交手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:13.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,不知為何　我並未恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:20.69,Default1,,0,0,0,,卻深感到痛徹心扉的悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:40.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,多少遇上了點麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:42.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,不過我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:46.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,聖石之種　No.XIV
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:53.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,或許　她的手中也有幾顆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:01.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,不要緊　我是不會猶豫的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:10.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,等著我　媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:15.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,我很快就會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.98,0:25:12.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,不管孩子還是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.06,0:25:15.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,都需要適當休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.67,0:25:19.36,Default1,,0,0,0,,所以　我們來到了當地的海鳴溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.95,0:25:23.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,在這平和的時光中　究竟是誰來打攪我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.95,0:25:28.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,神秘的黑衣少女究竟懷著怎樣的目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.00,0:25:32.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,下集　魔法少女奈葉　第五話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.05,0:25:35.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,這裡是溫泉勝地、海鳴溫泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.09,0:25:38.19,Default1,,0,0,0,,莉莉卡露瑪吉卡露　我會加油的
